text: haey yeung ban thveu aoy puokke klaytowchea anakdoeknea daembi changaoulobangheanh phlauv( dl mnoussa lok) tam batobanhchea robsa yeung . haey yeung ban phdal vea hi dl puokke aoy sang ampeula ning brate b tde sa lat haeyning brichcheak hsaa kat . haey puokke kuchea anak del ban korp sakkar mk champoh yeung
